item.description: CONTRIBUTORS Issues & PR’s Please fill out associated templates clearly and as detailed as possible for the requested actions. It is important that you articulate WHAT you are trying to do and WHY so your request will be considered. Before submission, search and review all open and previously closed tickets before opening another one. This saves everyone time! Guidelines Development environment expectation is NodeJS v16 LTS & npm >= 8.0.0 Versioning & releases are handled by CI/CD & semantic versioning construct which relies upon semantic commits.
